        trt:deprecates            <http://taxon-concept.plazi.org/id/Plantae/Myrtus_punicifolia_Kunth_2010> , <http://taxon-concept.plazi.org/id/Animalia/Eugenia_neogracilis_Mazine_2010> , <http://taxon-concept.plazi.org/id/Plantae/Eugenia_rufoflavescens_Mattos_2000> , <http://taxon-concept.plazi.org/id/Animalia/Eugenia_schadrackiana_Legrand_1961> , <http://taxon-concept.plazi.org/id/Plantae/Eugenia_punicifolia_DC._2010> , <http://taxon-concept.plazi.org/id/Animalia/Eugenia_malacantha_Legrand_1961> , <http://taxon-concept.plazi.org/id/Animalia/Eugenia_duckeana_Mattos_1969> , <http://taxon-concept.plazi.org/id/Animalia/Eugenia_neonitida_Sobral_1995> ;
